  <!--
    CUDA configuration (version-switchable):
    - By default uses CUDA 13.1 (as before)
    - Can be overridden via MSBuild:
        /p:CudaToolkitVersion=11.8
        /p:CudaToolkitDir="C:\Program Files\NVIDIA GPU Computing Toolkit\CUDA\v11.8"
        /p:CudaToolkitCustomDir="C:\Program Files\NVIDIA GPU Computing Toolkit\CUDA\v11.8"
